30
00:01:52,160 --> 00:01:53,410
Don't go if you don't want to.

31
00:01:53,410 --> 00:01:55,520
I'll go alone.

32
00:01:55,520 --> 00:01:57,620
You can't just say that, you bastard!

33
00:01:57,620 --> 00:02:00,100
