67
00:04:19,020 --> 00:04:20,590
So, tell me now, okay?

68
00:04:20,590 --> 00:04:23,550
Tell me why you guys came in here.

69
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:35,570
Shit...

70
00:04:37,550 --> 00:04:39,430
Shit.

71
