78
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:09,280
Let go, you pervert!

79
00:05:09,280 --> 00:05:12,330
Shit. How embarrassing.

80
00:05:12,330 --> 00:05:14,550
Wow, you have a pretty face,

81
00:05:14,550 --> 00:05:16,310
