249
00:19:09,500 --> 00:19:11,590
But you're too weak.

250
00:19:11,590 --> 00:19:12,970
What?

251
00:19:14,410 --> 00:19:16,700
You tried to ruin

252
00:19:16,700 --> 00:19:19,150
